339
00:12:33.020 --> 00:12:34.855
- And did you see
this person's face?

340
00:12:34.888 --> 00:12:36.457
- No.

341
00:12:36.490 --> 00:12:37.958
- Well. I appreciate the fact
that you've been honest

342
00:12:37.992 --> 00:12:39.927
