417
00:15:32.667 --> 00:15:34.234
What's going on?

418
00:15:34.268 --> 00:15:35.637
- Yeah. there seems
to be a disconnect.

419
00:15:35.670 --> 00:15:37.304
The whole Valentine's Day
element--

420
00:15:37.337 --> 00:15:39.541
