433
00:16:01.328 --> 00:16:02.362
- Oh. my gosh.

434
00:16:02.396 --> 00:16:04.164
Okay. um.
so I'll try and be quick.

435
00:16:04.198 --> 00:16:06.668
Um. I remember Tim
